{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Before he became SS, he was actually drafted to this, as he was not a too young man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he indicated certain sympathy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was in very good relations, so my uncle put his life in his hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was Pfiffiger and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Pfiffiger was the nice guy, and [NON-ENGLISH] was the devil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I'll explain to you why he was the devil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he met with him and he told him that he has his daughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told him I have here the daughter-- my daughter, and I'm sure that you also have children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, the tides was already changing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the chairman, some of them who had a little bit more foresight, they saw that Hitler is not going to go too long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he tried to befriend my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told him that's he's going to try to help him out, help him in carrying out this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle told him the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put it plain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, look, if it's going to happen, it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have no choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to bring in the bread with two horses and carriages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they used to take out the empty bags out from the ghetto in order to reload them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we gave-- I gave my cousin a sleeping pill, which the German gave it to us in order to give her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we put her under the bags, and we brought her out through the gates.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, she met this lady, this rabbi's wife, turned her over to a Lithuanian family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another child with us, and was also turned over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And unfortunately, the older child was turned over to the Germans, and they killed him.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
